store:
CREATE TABLE store (
  s_company_id integer,
  s_division_id integer,
  s_market_id integer,
  s_floor_space integer,
  s_number_employees integer,
  s_closed_date_sk integer,
  s_store_sk integer,
  s_zip character,
  s_state character,
  s_suite_number character,
  s_street_type character,
  s_hours character,
  s_store_id character,
  s_country character varying,
  s_county character varying,
  s_city character varying,
  s_street_name character varying,
  s_street_number character varying,
  s_company_name character varying,
  s_division_name character varying,
  s_market_manager character varying,
  s_market_desc character varying,
  s_geography_class character varying,
  s_manager character varying,
  s_store_name character varying,
  s_rec_end_date date,
  s_rec_start_date date,
  s_tax_precentage numeric,
  s_gmt_offset numeric
);

CREATE UNIQUE INDEX store_pkey ON store USING btree (s_store_sk);
customer:
CREATE TABLE customer (
  c_last_review_date_sk integer,
  c_birth_year integer,
  c_birth_month integer,
  c_birth_day integer,
  c_first_sales_date_sk integer,
  c_first_shipto_date_sk integer,
  c_current_addr_sk integer,
  c_current_hdemo_sk integer,
  c_current_cdemo_sk integer,
  c_customer_sk integer,
  c_email_address character,
  c_login character,
  c_preferred_cust_flag character,
  c_last_name character,
  c_first_name character,
  c_salutation character,
  c_customer_id character,
  c_birth_country character varying
);

CREATE UNIQUE INDEX customer_pkey ON customer USING btree (c_customer_sk);
store_returns:
CREATE TABLE store_returns (
  sr_return_quantity integer,
  sr_reason_sk integer,
  sr_store_sk integer,
  sr_addr_sk integer,
  sr_hdemo_sk integer,
  sr_cdemo_sk integer,
  sr_customer_sk integer,
  sr_item_sk integer,
  sr_return_time_sk integer,
  sr_returned_date_sk integer,
  sr_net_loss numeric,
  sr_store_credit numeric,
  sr_reversed_charge numeric,
  sr_refunded_cash numeric,
  sr_return_ship_cost numeric,
  sr_fee numeric,
  sr_return_amt_inc_tax numeric,
  sr_return_tax numeric,
  sr_return_amt numeric,
  sr_ticket_number bigint
);

CREATE UNIQUE INDEX store_returns_pkey ON store_returns USING btree (sr_item_sk, sr_ticket_number);
